songs.title: Freak On (Original)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Teyana Taylor]
Oh, oh, oh
(Mustard on the beat ho)

[Verse 1: Teyana Taylor]
We're gone, we're gone
I'm right inside of the candy store, be mine
I'm every flavor, eat it up
Cherry chocolate, beat it up
Don't be shy, let's get down to the point tonight

[Pre-Chorus: Teyana Taylor]
Oh, we can be backseat, now I'll give it up
I'll do it any type of way, no matter, just fill me up

[Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
Oh, 'cause I will be your freak all through the day, until the dawn
And I can do whatever (Bop, bop) thing you like, boy, what you want? (Oh, yeah)
'Cause we ain't gotta tell nobody (Nobody)
We ain't gotta tell nobody
'Cause it goes on and on and on
On and on and on, yeah

[Verse 2: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
I'm up and you up
Don't make me wait for that shit that I need in my life
I'll slide it to the side, let's go
Dim the lights so it don't show
Oh, I, I be so ready all the time

[Pre-Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
Oh, we can be backseat, now I'll give it up (Oh)
I'll do it any type of way, no matter, just fill me up

[Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
Oh, 'cause I will be your freak all through the day, until the dawn (Ooh)
And I can do whatever (Bop, bop) thing you like, boy, what you want? (Oh, yeah)
'Cause we ain't gotta tell nobody (Nobody)
We ain't gotta tell nobody (Nobody)
'Cause it goes on and on and on
On and on and on, yeah

[Post-Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
On and on and on, on and on and on
On and on and on
We just go on and on and on, on and on and on
On and on and on, yeah

[Verse 3: Chris Brown]
I'm horny, you horny (Alright)
We making love from the bed to the floor tonight
You got me feigning, wanting more, beat it up, you on all fours
Don't know why, I be so ready all the time
Oh, we can role play, spread your legs, I'll eat it up (Girl, I)
Girl, I'ma make love to your mind when I beat it up
Girl, I need you, I need you
I need you to pop that thang for me
I know that you and your girls all some freaks (Oh, yeah)

[Pre-Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
So, we can be backseat, now I'll give it up (Oh, woah)
I'll do it any type of way, no matter, just fill me up (Huh, huh, ow!)

[Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
Oh, 'cause I will be your freak all through the day, until the dawn (Ooh)
And I can do whatever (Bop, bop) thing you like, boy, what you want? (Oh, yeah)
'Cause we ain't gotta tell nobody (Nobody)
We ain't gotta tell nobody (Nobody)
'Cause it goes on and on and on
On and on and on, yeah

[Post-Chorus: Teyana Taylor & Chris Brown]
On and on and on, on and on and on
On and on and on
We just go on and on and on, on and on and on
On and on and on, yeah
